  <name>YZZO - Clipboard Manager</name>
  <summary>A clipboard manager built for simplicity and productivity.</summary>

  <developer id="app.yzzo">
    <name>Lucca Romaniello</name>
  </developer>

  <description>
    <p>
      YZZO is a clipboard manager built for simplicity and productivity.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Simple: Automatically saves text and images you copy. Easily find and paste anything from your history.</li>
      <li>Customizable: Set up global hotkeys for instant access. Choose between light and dark themes.</li>
      <li>Private: No analytics, no telemetry, no tracking. Your clipboard history is stored locally on your device.</li>
      <li>YZZO is open-source. This Flathub version supports ongoing development.</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

